reviewText: Bought this for a gift for my niece and nephew. They loved it!
This Dvd only has 3 episodes, compared to the other Dvds that have about 5-6 episodes. That was a bit disappointing.

This DVD contains three episodes from the Wow! Wow! Wubbzy! cartoon. Amazon doesn't always do a good job on their DVD episode listings so here are the episodes that are included on this DVD:

1. Mr. Valentine
2. Cupid's Little Helper
3. My Speedy Valentine
Got this for my 2 year old that loves Wubbzy. He loved the video and is ready for Valentine's day!
thanks so much very awesome, arrived on time, would purchase from again and would reccommend to friends and family. thanks
My boys love these Valentine inspired episodes but it is not the normal length of a Wubbzy DVD. It is only 3 episodes. As long as you expect that then it is great.
Excellent Video.  I bought it to teach my daughter about Valentines Day on a level she could understand.  Worked great.  She also loves Wubbzy.  My 8 year old twins also quiety enjoyed watching it.
